 engage with the literacy education of local children  including partnerships with Waddell Elementary School in Lexington  VA  and Rockbridge Reads in Rockbridge County  VA  Additionally  MAJ Iddings serves as the Programs Coordinator of the VMI Center for Undergraduate Research  VCUR  where he coordinates the VCUR Symposium and the Summer Undergraduate Research Institute  SURI Arts   Humanities Division ERHS Home Degrees   Programs Courses Honors in English Intro to New Faculty English Advising Creative Arts Contest Departmental Activities Academic Links Faculty Peggy Herring Administrative Assistant English  Rhetoric    Humanistic Studies P 540  464 7240 F 540  464 7779 227 Scott Shipp Hall Lexington  VA  24450  email to  english vmi edu  Arts   Humanities Division ERHS Home Degrees   Programs Courses Honors in English Intro to New Faculty English Advising Creative Arts Contest Departmental Activities Academic Links Faculty Peggy Herring Administrative Assistant English  Rhetoric    Humanistic Studies P 540  464 7240 F 540  464 7779 227 Scott Shipp Hall Lexington  VA  24450  email to  english vmi edu Arts   Humanities Division ERHS Home Degrees   Programs Courses Honors in English Intro to New Faculty English Advising Creative Arts Contest Departmental Activities Academic Links Faculty Arts   Humanities Division Arts   Humanities Division ERHS Home ERHS Home Degrees   Programs Degrees   Programs Courses Courses Honors in English Honors in English Intro to New Faculty Intro to New Faculty English Advising English Advising Creative Arts Contest Creative Arts Contest Departmental Activities Departmental Activities Academic Links Academic Links Faculty Faculty Peggy Herring Administrative Assistant English  Rhetoric    Humanistic Studies P 540  464 7240 F 540  464 7779 227 Scott Shipp Hall Lexington  VA  24450  email to  english vmi edu Peggy Herring Administrative Assistant English  Rhetoric    Humanistic Studies P 540  464 7240 F 540  464 7779 227 Scott Shipp Hall L